{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23172.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810600,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":210502,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day17.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime02","chara":[{"id":810600,"motion":100}],"nameAvRight":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Well then, I'd better get going.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":210502}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Bye, Hitomi!"},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":100}],"nameAvCenter":"Sayaka","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Thanks for coming to celebrate with me!","textAvColor":"textSayaka"},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":810600}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You too, Madoka.@Thanks for putting all this together."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":210502,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Of course!@I'm just sorry we couldn't do it sooner."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Those other girls helping out...they were@your Magical Girl buddies, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":210502,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Ah...yeah."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So it's true, then.@You made a contract."},{"chara":[{"id":210502}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I wasn't trying to hide it, I swear―@I just...never found the right time to say it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":210502,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I'm sorry.@I know how against it you were..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Nah, I'm the one who should say sorry.@I didn't exactly make it easy to bring up."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But you know―I'm not against it anymore.@Not at all."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":210502,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Wait...really?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I never told you, but when I was in the hospital...@I kinda got caught up in a Witch's Labyrinth."},{"chara":[{"id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Some Magical Girl I didn't know@showed up and saved me."},{"chara":[{"id":210502,"motion":400}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Oh. Really?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":200401,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yeah.@I didn't even have time to thank her..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I mean, I totally froze up. I was too@scared to even think about fighting."},{"chara":[{"id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But still―someone risked herself@to save me. I can't exactly go around@badmouthing Magical Girls after that."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":210502,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Sayaka..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]And hey, you're not doing it alone, right?@You've got backup."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":210502,"motion":201,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Yeah! Homura and Mabayu are both@really strong―it's amazing!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":210502}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So don't worry about me!@I'll be just fine."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Then the peace of Mitakihara is in your hands,@Madoka Kaname! Us civilians are counting on you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":210502,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Ha ha ha..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":1,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":210502}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Oh yeah.@That reminds me―"},{"chara":[{"id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]When you contracted,@you had to make a wish, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]What did you end up wishing for?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":210502,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Uh, well..."},{"chara":[{"id":210502}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It's a little hard to explain..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":210502}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I just um...wanted to help someone who had@lost everything. To give her a little hope..."},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":400}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20][chara:200401:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Wait―for real?!@What are you, some kind of saint?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":210502,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I-it's not that weird..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]All praise Madoka―our holy savior!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":210502,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Come on, quit it!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":100}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Wait, no joke―I think my arm just@started healing! It's a miracle!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":210502}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Geez..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
